289
00:16:56,703 --> 00:16:58,183
He deceived you,

290
00:16:58,543 --> 00:17:00,024
looked down on you,

291
00:17:00,264 --> 00:17:02,943
and used every means
to drive you out of Jiuyi Mountain.

292
00:17:03,264 --> 00:17:05,624
