to absorb resentment.

330
00:20:18,744 --> 00:20:20,583
Gong Gong struck Buzhou Mountain,
which caused great destruction.

331
00:20:20,744 --> 00:20:21,784
When Nuwa Goddess repaired the sky,

332
00:20:22,184 --> 00:20:23,903
