483
00:29:12,704 --> 00:29:13,303
Hey, you.

484
00:29:13,984 --> 00:29:14,903
Don't follow me.

485
00:29:56,464 --> 00:29:58,383
Then I'll go ahead.

486
00:30:00,024 --> 00:30:00,704
Farewell.

