545
00:36:17,983 --> 00:36:19,264
and help us cross to the other side.

546
00:36:20,144 --> 00:36:22,503
But doubts,

547
00:36:22,863 --> 00:36:23,624
suspicions,

548
00:36:23,983 --> 00:36:25,023
and lies in people's hearts

549
00:36:25,503 --> 00:36:28,184
